Zagazig Cemetery.—The lottery organised in aid of the above cemetery was
                        drawn on Sunday, the following being the winning numbers : 1st prize, 384 ;
                        2nd, 682 ; 3rd, 364. the proceeds of the lottery amount to about £15.

Best and most comfortable, unique for its position on Nile bank. Under German
